name: Welcome to my site
body:
### Welcome to Wu Yuyan's site
This is my first time using automatic page generator to create pages for all of my owm. To be honest, it has been a geat torture foe me to figure out how the Github works. But finally, hooh, I have my personal site now!

## Who am I?
An ordinary teenager with great passion for exploring the amazing world.


![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xiaobailin/xiaobailin.github.io/master/images/default.jpg)

A student trying to get over obstacles to become a programmer.


![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xiaobailin/xiaobailin.github.io/master/default.jpg)

A girl who never changes her love for food, no matter what happens.


![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xiaobailin/HTML/master/images/default.jpeg)

###*English lecture/debate*

###*PhotoShop*

## What I want to be?
I wanna be a person who tries her best for every thing.
###**Life is a journey**
                       ————Jack London
From the hell to the heaven 

There's no straight way to walk 

Sometimes up ,sometimes down 

Hope give a heaven for us 

Despair makes a hell for us 

Some choices are waiting for me 

Which one on earth is better 

No god in the world can help me 

Choosing is the byname of freedom 

Different choice makes different future 

It's stupid to put eyes on others 

I have to make up on my own mind 

Going my way to the destination 

Facing success or failure 

It's no need to care too much 

Only if i've tired my best 

It's enough for my simple life
